{
  "stem": "19231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Germans-- the Russians came in, marched in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Poland, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- the Russian, I remember, marched in with tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were throwing food and chocolate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we thought that we will go home with them, that they will go take-- take the whole Poland and we be able to go home with them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they just occupied the half of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed under occupation from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we occupied-- it was an empty building some place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was it a school or something?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from-- the people from-- maybe there were 30 of us 35-- all occupied this empty place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were-- we stayed there for quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I think there was a-- like a little black-- started like a black market.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they start like buying some liquor and taking to a different town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- that's how I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how we survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little bit trading and this and that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trading, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe six, seven months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I came-- we found out that from Germany to-- it was like a delegation from Germany came into a town, which was also not too far from the town we were.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were registrating people who wants to go back, the people that ran away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to take back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So a lot of people, they were standing in the line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were registrating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a lot of them went home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know a lot of the people that we left together on the bus, they went back home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father and my mom, we wanted to go back very much so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we wanted to be with the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
